      "subsection_title": "Initial Steps to Publish (Registration)",
      "text": "Section: Manuscripts and Publishing Process\nSubsection: Initial Steps to Publish (Registration)\nTags: manuscript, publishing, submission, journal selection\nContent: To publish a manuscript: 1. Select the journal where you want to submit your manuscript. 2. Since it is your first submission to this journal, register yourself on the journal's platform. 3. During registration, provide all required information such as: Name, Affiliation, Other necessary details. 4. Complete registration by clicking the finish button. After registration, go to the journal's main page and: 1. Click on 'Submit the paper'. 2. Login using your username and password. 3. Access your author dashboard and start submitting your manuscript.\nKey points: Select journal; Register on platform; Provide name and affiliation; Login and access author dashboard"
    },
