      "subsection_title": "Introduction Section Details",
      "text": "Section: Manuscript Writing and Structure (IMRD)\nSubsection: Introduction Section Details\nTags: IMRD, scientific writing, manuscript structure, six S's\nContent: In the Introduction, the goal is to focus the reader's attention amid many distractions and provide: Background of the research area. Identification of knowledge gaps. The rationale for the study. Specific objectives the research seeks to answer. This section sets the context and prepares the reader for the study's importance.\nKey points: Provide background; Identify knowledge gaps; State rationale; Define specific objectives"
    },
